{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your order of knights has been slaying dragons for generations. Now, only the Queen remains and you have been chosen to eradicate her. However, at the peak of the sacred forge, the confrontation will not go as expected\u2026</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hopeguard is a third-person dark fantasy game centered on the themes of loss and acceptance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Journey through caves, ruins and forests to solve environmental puzzles and fulfill your quest\u2014but with a new perspective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>YOUR CORNERED NEMESIS</strong></u>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the last of her kind, the Dragon Queen fights with the desperation of a dying breed. Could it be that she resists so fiercely to protect something precious?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474510/extras/DragonBeatyshotGIF.gif?t=1739580328\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>WITNESS THE REMNANTS OF WAR</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Hopeguard knights have paid a heavy price in their ancestral hunt. Finding an alternative path through the ruins won\u2019t always be easy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474510/extras/PaysageGIF.gif?t=1739580328\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>MY FAINFUL SHIELD!</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are trained to survive and your shield has saved your life countless times.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>THE SACRED CRYSTALS GUIDE THE WAY</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ancient, dormant magical mechanisms can be reactivated, but they will clearly need to be realigned.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>TRAVEL BROADENS THE MIND</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on an introspective journey of questioning traditions and preconceived notions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474510/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739580328","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474510/page.bg.jpg?t=1739580328","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474510/60a669ce0972864e8b303c479672e6da7d665e26/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739580328","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474510/60a669ce0972864e8b303c479672e6da7d665e26/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739580328","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your order of knights has been slaying dragons for generations. Now, only the Queen remains and you have been chosen to eradicate her. However, at the peak of the sacred forge, the confrontation will not go as expected\u2026</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hopeguard is a third-person dark fantasy game centered on the themes of loss and acceptance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Journey through caves, ruins and forests to solve environmental puzzles and fulfill your quest\u2014but with a new perspective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>YOUR CORNERED NEMESIS</strong></u>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the last of her kind, the Dragon Queen fights with the desperation of a dying breed. Could it be that she resists so fiercely to protect something precious?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474510/extras/DragonBeatyshotGIF.gif?t=1739580328\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>WITNESS THE REMNANTS OF WAR</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Hopeguard knights have paid a heavy price in their ancestral hunt. Finding an alternative path through the ruins won\u2019t always be easy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474510/extras/PaysageGIF.gif?t=1739580328\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>MY FAINFUL SHIELD!</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are trained to survive and your shield has saved your life countless times.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>THE SACRED CRYSTALS GUIDE THE WAY</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ancient, dormant magical mechanisms can be reactivated, but they will clearly need to be realigned.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>TRAVEL BROADENS THE MIND</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on an introspective journey of questioning traditions and preconceived notions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","developers":["Hopesquad Studio"],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Free To Play","id":"37"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474510/header.jpg?t=1739580328","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":[],"ma